asset.author: HamiltonBeachBrands
asset.hookText:
Each day you're forced to choose a side— Single-serve packs, like K-Cup Packs or ground coffee.
But now you can have both -- with any FlexBrew from Hamilton Beach.
For 40% less than a Keurig Mini Plus Brewer you can easily brew a single serve pack or ground coffee.
Just place, or scoop, and brew.
FlexBrew's advanced brewing process delivers better extraction than a Keurig Mini Plus Brewing System for a delicious flavor-filled cup, every time..
And every FlexBrew lets you enjoy a to-go-mug or at-home-mug.
With the 2-way FlexBrew model you can brew a single cup or a whole pot. Even program your brew time.
Thanks to FlexBrew, choosing sides is over. Now you're free to enjoy maximum brewing flexibility.
Hamilton Beach. Good Thinking.
